# Bubble wrap (parallel track)

**Goal:** 0 → ~1k followers per growth account. **Not** affiliate product videos (Modules 3–8).

Source: `data/research/course/BUBBLE_WRAP.md`

## Does NOT block affiliate

Affiliate launch needs: purchased account + FastMoss + Kling + Zernio — **no phones required**.

Bubble hardware (4 phones + HP hub) can lag weeks behind affiliate posting.

## Format (locked)

- **2-slide TikTok photo slideshow** every post
- Slide 1: subject in bubble wrap + hook text only
- Slide 2: Pause/Follow/Share/Comment pop interaction lines
- **Mackenzie sound** required: see `BUBBLE_WRAP.md` for URL

## Account cadence (`accounts.json`)

| Cadence | Posts/day |
|---------|-----------|
| Safe (phone_1, phone_4) | 3–4 |
| Aggressive (phone_2, phone_3) | 8–10 |

Post via Zernio on bubble IDs — **never** post affiliate clips to bubble accounts or vice versa.

## Hub laptop (later)

WSL Ubuntu on owner HP → optional Tailscale SSH for agent terminal.  
Affiliate keys (FastMoss, Kling) stay on **cloud VM**; hub needs `ZERNIO_API_TOKEN` for bubble publish when worker exists.

## When owner asks about phones / Ubuntu / hub

Read install docs — report **one** next step in plain English. Do not merge bubble creative into affiliate pipeline rules.

